Classes/LOTAnimatedImage.html.name: LOTAnimatedImage
Classes/LOTAnimatedImage.html.abstract: A wrapper class to allow LOTComposition to be compatible for SDWebImage loading/cache/rendering system. The GIF image loading from LOTCompositionView+WebCache category, will use this subclass instead of UIImage.
